title: Unemployment rate in Malawi 2019
summary: Overall Unemployment rate has decreased over the Year.
Unemployment rate is slightly decreasing from 2006 to 2007, slightly increasing from 2007 to 2008, roughly constant from 2008 to 2011, and lastly slightly decreasing from 2011 to 2012.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2006 and 2007.
The highest Unemployment rate, of value 7.09 was reached at Year 2006
Minimum Unemployment rate about 6.18 was reached at Year 2008, and 2012
